{"type": "article", "id": 35460, "title": "利用拼接，这面镜子可以浮起来｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-11T23:07:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35687, "name": "HYFEN"}, {"id": 35688, "name": "PEDERJESSEN"}, {"id": 35689, "name": "Matar"}, {"id": 35690, "name": "Isabel de Peque"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161211224103dLmy6SxCBWpI9er1.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>IsoGrid by Jojo Chuang</h3><p>利用视觉错觉打造的设计并不少见，台湾设计师 Jojo Chuang 最近为美国家居品牌 <a href=\"http://thehyfen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HYFEN</a> 打造的墙面镜 IsoGrid 就借助形状和不同材质的拼接，让人不得不定神仔细观察一番。菱形镜面左右下方可以和大理石板或是单色的嵌板自由组合在一起，相当百搭。这是它的<a href=\"http://thehyfen.com/iso-series/isogrid-mirror\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 170 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112241193r4TRk8By10cbiIq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224119rZVn2W6eQj5wE8Oq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224119J8Tcp9atwI6zLXWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224119gKjBCpiVPnl4JDOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oil &amp; Vinegar Cruets by NYcruets</h3><p>厌倦了厨房里一字排开的瓶瓶罐罐？调料瓶制造商 <a href=\"http://www.nycruets.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NYcruets</a> 制作的二合一瓶子会让你的台面更有艺术气息。在大一号的油瓶内部还有一个造型独特的小号醋瓶，两者都是由匈牙利北部的工匠吹制而成的。注入一黑一黄两种颜色之后，放在台面上作为装饰也相当抢眼。这是它的<a href=\"http://nycruets.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 49 到 69 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112244052UlmyGqevnjAp5Jd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224406hAHbWden6aSiLl0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224406QWiYZK382gn1yfuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ray by PEDERJESSEN</h3><p>丹麦工作室 <a href=\"http://pederjessen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PEDERJESSEN</a> 最近为设计品牌 <a href=\"http://materdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matar</a> 打造了一套融合了金属和木材的灯具系列 Ray，包括了台灯、吊灯和墙面灯三种款式。它们的造型都相当简洁，半圆形金属灯罩内还有一圈橡木罩子，在磁铁的帮助下能够自由调整地光线照射的角度。这是它的<a href=\"http://materdesign.com/search?type=product&amp;q=Ray\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 895 到 2295 丹麦克朗不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224327sgDVtyBa9bPXQEu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.532813\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224327FNpXYnJxv9kl5fwP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224328treqUI3F0Af4HTJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224327y196qDpZxsotJdhO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ROAV</h3><p>为了让折叠太阳镜既好看又足够轻薄易携带，来自美国的设计团队带来了一款据称是世界上最薄的太阳眼镜 ROAV，在折叠状态下仅有 8.5 毫米厚，重量也只有 15.8 克。它的镜框采用离子镀的不锈钢，折叠处采用团队特别研发的无螺丝弹簧铰链设计，使用起来相当流畅。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/653457680/roav-anywhere-eyewear\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112243404ITmpleWjz8dgkX7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582353\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224340GwbucIr0ApOhK5Da.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224339faOdMmixVuRXG9E3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224340pTSHvbjMDt1GQreU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.791176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224340oHgKQqyc9xAChU7X.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>AirSelfie</h3><p>为了克服限制拍出好看的照片，继自拍杆、可粘式摄像头和能够 360 度旋转的手机架之后，一个由多国设计师组成的团队研发了这款号称世界上最小的便携式自拍无人机 AirSelfie。它的便携是通过配套的手机壳达成的，而且当你将机器放在手机壳中时它还会自动充电。使用时将它从手机壳中取出，在对应的手机 App 中选择所需的飞行模式进行拍摄即可，所有的照片都会通过无线网络同步到手机中。AirSelfie 的像素为 500 万，储存空间 4 GB。美中不足的是它仅支持五种手机型号，三分钟的续航能力并不适合长时间拍摄。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1733117980/airselfie\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 224 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224209IDbeCkVWvcZjginL.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224209VhCsjp6qB2XK9lSN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112242081VIJPUvAprY7XkFs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Choco &amp; Co Special Edition by Isabel de Peque</h3><p>以建筑物为主题设计的巧克力包装并不少见，我们之前就曾介绍过一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32133.html\">以当地特色的门为灵感</a>设计的包装。西班牙设计师 <a href=\"http://www.isabeldepeque.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Isabel de Peque</a> 为巧克力品牌 Choco &amp; Co 设计的包装则是把城市、建材和巧克力的风味融合在了一起。看似毫无规律的组合并没有想象中的那么不协调：比如黑巧克力就选择了马德里的石材，牛奶巧克力则是伦敦的砖材，别有一番风味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112242421pw7AJSdW3yzZCuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224243e569lQTIPAivG1FJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161211224242we6z3gariTCBZk8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112242422dAWQvzenEXM8V1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612112242437FiAHJmhdRGyfpgB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}